
                    ---------------------
                    title
                    ---------------------
                    guid (PK)
		    title
		    title_type (Movie | TV)
		    release_year
                    genre
                    sub_genre
		    seasons (nullable)
		    episodes (nullable)
		    created_date
		    modified_date

                    ---------------------
                    media_item
                    ---------------------
                    guid (PK)
                    title_guid (FK)
                    collection_guid (FK)
		    media_type (dvd, dvd10, vhs, blueray, ultrahd4k)
		    edition
		    distribution_year
		    media_item_image_url_front
		    media_item_image_url_back
		    distributor
		    upc
		    created_date
		    modified_date
                    purchase_date
                    purchase_price	
		    grade_text	
		    grade_rubric
		    grading_company
		    graded_date
		    condition (sealed, complete, used)

                    ---------------------
                    collection
                    ---------------------
                    guid (PK)
		    volume
		    edition
		    theme
                    serial_number
                    nfc_token
		    created_date
		    modified_date
		    collection_nft_image_url
		    cover_nft_image_url_front
		    cover_nft_image_url_back
		    cover_nft_image_url_spine

                    ---------------------
                    listing
                    ---------------------
                    guid (PK)
                    collection_guid (FK)
		    list_date
		    sale_date
		    sale_price
		    list_price
		    listing_url
		    marketplace
		    listing_id
		    status (listed, unlisted)
		    created_date
		    modified_date

                    ---------------------
                    authentication_log
                    ---------------------
		    guid
		    collection_guid
		    scan_time
		    result
		    worker_version
		    ip_country
		    ip_address
		    device
		    browser
		    referrer
		    response_time_ms

                    ---------------------
                    audit_log
                    ---------------------
		    guid
		    table_name
		    record_guid
		    action
		    old_value
		    new_value
		    user_guid
		    created_date
		    deleted_date
		    modified_date




